106}, "last_reply_by": "Jen312", "last_touched": 1730782930, "title": "老婆在家除了带孩子，还能做点什么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1086705", "created": 1730773208, "deleted": 0, "content": "事情起因是老婆说在家太无聊，娃送去上学后一天有 3 、4 个小时空档期\r\n\r\n她总觉得可以做点事情，赚点小钱补贴家用（我是倾向于在家专职带娃）。\r\n\r\n昨天还出去跑了两单外卖……被我说了一顿，我怕她还整什么其他事情\r\n\r\n想听听广大 V 友有什么好建议？", "content_rendered": "<p>事情起因是老婆说在家太无聊，娃送去上学后一天有 3 、4 个小时空档期</p>\n<p>她总觉得可以做点事情，赚点小钱补贴家用（我是倾向于在家专职带娃）。</p>\n<p>昨天还出去跑了两单外卖……被我说了一顿，我怕她还整什么其他事情</p>\n<p>想听听广大 V 友有什么好建议？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730773208, "replies": 55, "id": 1086705}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1724399301", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1724399301", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 8006, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1724399301", "stars": 6427, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 622778, "username": "falser101", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/falser101", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aeb629d7082b7f2f166ed7da8ae0366f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aeb629d7082b7f2f166ed7da8ae0366f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aeb629d7082b7f2f166ed7da8ae0366f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1680773602, "last_modified": 1723701277}, "last_reply_by": "youyouzi", "last_touched": 1730778902, "title": "Linux 微信 4.0 来了！牛逼", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1086523", "created": 1730709555, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://bbs.deepin.org/post/280772", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://bbs.deepin